-- Ecobank Ghana says half year 2014 net profit up 91.2 pct 
-- By Kwasi Kpodo
-- Wed Jul 30, 2014 06:31AM EDT
-- None



ACCRA, July 30 (Reuters) - Ecobank Ghana Limited <EBG.GH>, the local unit of pan-African bank Ecobank, said on Wednesday its net profit for the six months through to June rose 91.2 percent to 153,947 million cedis ($44.5 million) compared with 80,487 million cedis a year ago.

